column5: stoty and I the bay sunday managed only one big girl to hit but she was a beauty and my pb 12.52lbs 31.5long and 18.5girth
Nice fish - congrats. Didn't happen to see Fishnsled's boat nearby did ya?
Nice hawg!  That's worth it anyday
Nice tanker !!!!! ... Congrats on the pb.... A trophy for sure...
That's a great looking eye! Congrats on the PB
I've caught my fair share of walleye and your fish is about 6lbs heavier than my PB ....well done!

Nice fish. speaking of Walleye has anyone been on the Ottawa River of late. I have been out twice this week and have been putting a beaten on them. Probably 20 fish in 6 hrs of fishing and the largest was 25 inch and the smallest about 18 inch. There deep 30 to 35 ft. Trolling TD-11 and reefers. Gold and black combo seems to be the hot colour. Sorry for h-jacking your thread.
PB's are always a good thing - thanks for showing us your PB.  David  aka  Superdad
